quran[8{c,v,t}:
5,24,"lekin onhon ne phir yahi kaha ke"" ae moose! hum to wahan kabhi nah jayen ge jab taq woh wahan mojood hain bas tum aur tumhara rab, dono jao aur lrho, hum yahan baithy hain """
5,25,"is par moose ne kaha"" ae mere rab, mere ikhtiyar mein koi nahi magar ya meri apni zaat ya mera bhai, pas to hamein inn nafarman logon se allag kar day """
5,26,"Allah ne jawab diya"" acha to woh malik chalees saal taq inn par haraam hai, yeh zameen mein maaray maaray phrin ge, inn na farmanoon ki haalat par hargiz taras nah khao """
5,27,"aur zara inhen aadam ke do beton ka qissa bhi be kam o kaast suna do jab unn dono ne qurbani ki to un mein se aik ki qurbani qubool ki gayi aur dosray ki nah ki gayi uss ne kaha"" mein tujhe maar daloon ga"" is ne jawab diya"" Allah tomuttaqi yoo-n hi ki nazren qubool karta hai"
5,28,"agar to mujhe qatal karne ke liye haath uthaye ga to mein tujhe qatal karne ke liye haath nah uthaoun ga, mein Allah rab alameen se darta hon"
5,29,"mein chahta hon ke mera aur apna gunah to hi samaitt le aur dozakhi ban kar rahay zaalmon ke zulm ka yahi theek badla hai """
5,30,aakhir-kaar is ke nafs ne apne bhai ka qatal is ke liye aasaan kar diya aur woh usay maar kar unn logon mein shaamil ho gaya jo nuqsaan uthany walay hain
5,31,phir Allah ne aik kuaa bheja jo zameen khodnay laga taakay ussay betaye ke apne bhai ki laash kaisay chupaye yeh dekh kar woh bola afsos mujh par! mein is kaway jaissa bhi nah ho saka ke apne bhai ki laash chupaney ki tadbeer nikaal laita is ke baad woh apne kiye par bohat pchhta ya
